In this example, we've updated the `PointOfServiceAdapter` to extend `ListAdapter` and use the `DiffUtil` to efficiently update the list of items. We're also binding the `totalPOS` and `totalOrders` values to the corresponding views in the `pos_cardview.xml` layout file.

