The error "'when' branch is never reachable" is likely occurring because the Kotlin compiler is unable to determine that the `when` branches in your code are reachable. This can happen when the compiler cannot infer the possible types of the expression being matched in the `when` statement.

To resolve this issue, you can use the `when` subject syntax, which allows you to capture the value being matched in a variable and use that variable in the `when` branches.

Here's how you can modify your code to use the `when` subject syntax:

